Source.Name: openrct2
Source.Summary: A construction and management simulation video game that simulates amusement park management
Source.Description: OpenRCT2 is an open-source re-implementation of RollerCoaster Tycoon 2 (RCT2). The gameplay revolves around building and maintaining an amusement park containing attractions, shops and facilities. The player must try to make a profit and maintain a good park reputation whilst keeping the guests happy. OpenRCT2 allows for both scenario and sandbox play. Scenarios require the player to complete a certain objective in a set time limit whilst sandbox allows the player to build a more flexible park with optionally no restrictions or finance. Original RollerCoaster Tycoon 2 game files are required in order to play OpenRCT2.
